      <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">What We Look For</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-muted">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-accent mr-3 font-bold">â€¢</span>
            <span><strong>Curiosity:</strong> Genuine interest in robotics, research, engineering, or the scientific method.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-accent mr-3 font-bold">â€¢</span>
            <span><strong>Reliability:</strong> Commitment to attending meetings and following through on tasks.</span>
          </li>
