          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-accent mr-3 font-bold">â€¢</span>
            <span><strong>Prior Experience:</strong> Not requiredâ€”we mentor students at all levels. Coursework in robotics, programming, or controls is helpful but not necessary.</span>
          </li>
